scenes.description: Transition between songs with instrumental music.
Performance of the song 'Vampire' by DECO*27.
MC section where Subaru thanks the audience and comments on the choreography.

subtitles.original: 届かない人の街まで
subtitles.english: ...to the town of unreachable people.

subtitles.original: 始まりの終わりを伝えるために
subtitles.english: To convey the end of the beginning.

subtitles.original: 生きること　やめないこと
subtitles.english: To live, to not give up.

subtitles.original: あなたに今日　誇れるように
subtitles.english: So that I can be proud of myself to you today.

subtitles.original: 私なんてと　抱いてるんだろう
subtitles.english: I wonder if I'm embracing the words "someone like me".

subtitles.original: 誇りなんて　答えられたらいい
subtitles.english: What should I answer as "pride"?

subtitles.original: 言葉はいつでも　語るでもなくて
subtitles.english: Words are not always for speaking.

subtitles.original: そこにあるばかり　募るばかり
subtitles.english: They're just there, just growing.

subtitles.original: 私はあなたに　会いたくなるよ
subtitles.english: I'll want to see you.

subtitles.original: あたしヴァンパイア
subtitles.english: I'm a vampire.

subtitles.original: いいの？吸っちゃっていいの？
subtitles.english: Is it okay? Can I suck?

subtitles.original: 「もう無理もう無理」なんて　悪い子だね
subtitles.english: Saying "I can't take it anymore, I can't take it anymore". You're a bad kid.
(laughs)

subtitles.original: 最低最高　ずっと行き来してる
subtitles.english: Lowest, highest, going back and forth.

subtitles.original: 甘くなる不安の果実
subtitles.english: The sweetening fruit of anxiety.

subtitles.original: 誰かと居れば　それはたられば
subtitles.english: If I'm with someone, that's just a "what if".

subtitles.original: 強がってたって　気持ちにゃ逆らえない
subtitles.english: Even if I act tough, I can't go against my feelings.

subtitles.original: 離れていても　感じてるエモ
subtitles.english: Even if we're apart, I feel the "emo".

subtitles.original: 繋がってたしかめたら　死ねるかも
subtitles.english: If I confirm our connection, I might die.

subtitles.original: あたしヴァンパイア
subtitles.english: I'm a vampire.

subtitles.original: いいの？吸っちゃっていいの？
subtitles.english: Is it okay? Can I suck?

subtitles.original: 「もう無理もう無理」なんて　悪い子だね
subtitles.english: Saying "I can't take it anymore, I can't take it anymore". You're a bad kid.

subtitles.original: 試したいな　いっぱいで吐きたいな
subtitles.english: I want to try. I want to be full and spit it out.

subtitles.original: まだ絶対いけるよ
subtitles.english: I can still go, absolutely.

subtitles.original: 屈んじゃって待って
subtitles.english: Stooping down and waiting,

subtitles.original: 絡まっちゃって　これヤバい
subtitles.english: getting tangled up. This is bad.

subtitles.original: 肝心なとこ忘れたら　はじめまして
subtitles.english: If I forget the crucial part, then nice to meet you.

subtitles.original: 愛情ください　まだ絶対いけるよ
subtitles.english: Give me love. I can still go, absolutely.

subtitles.original: あたしヴァンパイア　まずはこっちおいで
subtitles.english: I'm a vampire. First, come over here.

subtitles.original: 内緒の思い　洗いざらい　吐き出したなら　正にお盛ん
subtitles.english: If I spit out all my secret thoughts, it's truly intense.

subtitles.original: 割り切れないけど　余りじゃない　そっと朝まで　通せんぼ
subtitles.english: It's not divisible but it's not a remainder. Quietly blocking the way until morning.

subtitles.original: 繰り返すやだ　わがままはタダ
subtitles.english: I don't want to repeat. Selfishness is free.

subtitles.original: 止まないもしも　叶えたいけど
subtitles.english: Even if the "what ifs" don't stop, I want them to come true.

subtitles.original: 君の全てを喰らうまで　いいじゃん
subtitles.english: Until I devour everything of yours, isn't it fine?

subtitles.original: 楽しんじゃん　気持ちいいじゃん
subtitles.english: Enjoy it, feels good, isn't it?
